<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><body style="font-family:Georgia,serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;color:#222;">
{% if is_beta %}
<div style="background:#fff8d6;padding:10px;border-left:4px solid #d4a843;">
🧪 <strong>Beta — your feedback shapes this.</strong> Reply with thoughts, suggestions, corrections, or topic ideas.
</div>
{% endif %}
<h1>{{ title }}</h1>
<div>{{ body | safe }}</div>

<h2>This week's drop</h2>
<p>{{ offer_pitch }}</p>
<p><a href="{{ product_url }}" style="background:#3d8a52;color:#fff;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;">{{ cta_text }}</a></p>
<p>Code: <strong>{{ coupon_code }}</strong> — {{ discount_pct }}% off, valid through {{ deadline }}.</p>

{% if personal_note %}
<hr>
<h3>Personal note</h3>
<p>{{ personal_note }}</p>
{% endif %}

<hr>
<p style="font-size:12px;color:#666;">💛 <strong>Pass it forward.</strong> Forward this to a friend — your code works for them too. We'll know you sent them.</p>
<p style="font-size:11px;color:#999;"><a href="{{ unsubscribe_url }}">Unsubscribe</a></p>
</body></html>
